{
  "stem": "7455.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So between the two of us, we did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I did Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Trunzer's room.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And when we were finished, I helped her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we were working on those brushes strapped to our feet, where you could dance on it to polish that parquet floors.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I found in her a friend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "She was a beautiful and a courageous woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Trunzer, I would go and fetch his dinner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I was allowed also to get some soup from the kitchen to bring-- to rush home during slow time to bring to my parents.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I was so grateful that my brothers were employed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And also they brought home some supplies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And in the meantime, they were-- now they came out with-- they say aktion, they call it, roundups of Jews, at that time to camps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But those were not-- at that time, we did not know about death camps, about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They came to the Judenrat, made a demand-- so many, let's say 500, Jews, 1,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "When I tell you that we had 22,000, population, they brought in from the adjoining villages Jews, which very few Jews were farmers or something, but they collected them and brought them into the ghetto, though the ghetto was more congested.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But at that time, there was no ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And-- I lose my trains of thought.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, roundup of Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they came, made demands to the Judenrat to provide 1,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a terrible function for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if they don't do it, the Ukrainians will do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They told them that it's to work camps, not death camps at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Perhaps they did not have death camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We did not know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they went from house to house unexpectedly and caught Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
